Ona Munson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ona_Munson 0 Ona Munson (born Owena Wolcott; June 16, 1903 – February 11, 1955) was an American actress perhaps best known for her portrayal of madam Belle Watling in Gone with the Wind (1939).
